<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Cloude Base</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            list-style: none;
            text-decoration: none;

            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;

            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.899);

            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            cursor: default;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar{
            background-color: transparent;
            width: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{
            background-color: rgba(76, 76, 76, 0.62);
            border-radius: 50px;
        }
        a,button {
            cursor: pointer;

            outline: none;
            border: none;
        }
        
        
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-start;

            position: relative;

            padding: 2vh 1vw;

            background-color: black;
        } 

        nav{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;

            position: sticky;
            z-index: 1;

            background-color: inherit;
            width: 100vw;

            top: 0px;

            padding: 16px 8px;

            border-radius: 10px;

        }

        .profileLogo{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;

            background-color: transparent;

            height: 100%;
            width: auto;

        }
        .profileLogo button {
            background-color: slateblue;

            color: white;
            
            padding: 10px;

            margin-right: 30px;

            border-radius: 5px;

            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.567);
            outline: none;
            border: none;

        }
        .profileLogo button a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        nav> h1 {
            font-size: 30px;
        }

        body>:nth-child(2){


            /* margin-top: 14vh; */
        }

        
        .section1 {
            width: 100%;

            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;

            background: linear-gradient(to top,transparent, rgba(105, 90, 205, 0.105), rgba(1, 88, 52, 0.35), rgba(0, 187, 255, 0.168), transparent);
        }
        .section1 header{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;

            padding: 4px 20px;

            background-color: transparent;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .section1 header a{

        }

        .allCategories {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;

            background-color: transparent;
            width: 100%;

            padding: 10px;
        }
        




       .detailForm{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;

        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 10px;

        width: 100%;
        
       }

       .detailForm form{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;

        border-radius: 30px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 245, 245, 0.04);

        background-color: rgba(60, 60, 60, 0.356);

        /* backdrop-filter: blur(40px); */
        /* width: max-content; */
        /* min-width: 300px; */

        color: white;
        padding: 30px;


       }

       .contsiner{
        width: 100%;
        margin: 10px;
       }



       .contsiner1, .contsiner2{

        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;

        background-color: transparent;

        width: 100%;


       }
       .contsiner1 input{
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(0, 73, 31), rgb(0, 34, 15));
        border: 2px solid rgb(20, 125, 66);
        border-radius: 8px;

        width: 210px;

        margin: 10px;
        padding: 10px;
        &::placeholder{
            font-size: 16px;
        }
       }


       .contsiner2 input{
        background: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(72, 73, 0), rgb(34, 21, 0));
        border: 2px solid rgb(163, 103, 19);
        border-radius: 8px;

        width: 210px;

        margin: 10px;
        padding: 10px;
        &::placeholder{
            font-size: 16px;
        }
       }
        




       .contsiner7{
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        flex-wrap: wrap;

        background-color: transparent;
        
       }
       .contsiner7 button{
        background: linear-gradient(-30deg, rgb(5, 80, 141), rgb(0, 33, 60));
        padding: 13px;
        border-radius: 7px;
        height: 50px;
        font-size: 19px;
        box-shadow: 10px 10px 20px black;

       }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <nav>

        <h1>Cloude Base</h1>
    
        <div class="profileLogo">

            <!-- <button>
                
                <a href="/upload"> Upload </a>
                <a href="">vaibhav999</a>
            </button> -->

            <button>
                
                <a href="/<%= userName %>"> <%= userName %> </a>
                <!-- <a href="">vaibhav999</a> -->
            </button>
            
        </div>

    </nav>

    <section class="section1">
        <header>
            <h3>Upload Movie to Cloud Base</h3>
            <!-- <a href="#">See all Categories</a> -->
        </header>

        <div class="allCategories">

            <p>Fille the form given below which collect some details about movie to help us to mantain database</p>
            <div class="detailForm">
                
                
                <form action="/upload/movie/files" method="POST">

                    <div class="contsiner1 contsiner">

                        <label for="poster">Upload poster image :</label>
                        <input type="file" name="poster" id="poster">
                    </div>

                    <div class="contsiner2 contsiner">

                        <label for="moviefile">Upload movie file :</label>
                        <input type="file" name="moviefile" id="moviefile">
                    </div>


                    <div class="contsiner7 contsiner">

                        <button type="submit">Upload files</button>
                    </div>

                </form>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>


    

    
    
</body>
</html>